FBIS4-29439 "dreas118_g_94003" FBIS-EAS-94-118 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 SOUTHEAST ASIA Burma Japanese Economic Mission Visits Japanese Economic Mission Visits Received by Than Shwe BK1706162894 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 17 Jun 94 BK1706162894 Rangoon Radio Burma Burmese BFN [Text] Senior General Than Shwe, chairman of the State Law and Order Restoration Council [SLORC] of the Union of Myanmar [Burma] and commander in chief of the Defense Services, received a visiting Japanese economic mission led by Mr. (Kazuo Haruna), vice chairman of the Keidanren entrepreneurs organization and chairman of the Marubeni Corporation, at the Defense Ministry's Dagon House at 1000 this morning. Also present on the occasion were Lieutenant General Khin Nyunt, SLORC secretary-1; Brigadier General Abel, minister of national planning and economic development; U Ohn Gyaw, minister of foreign affairs; Thura U Aung Htet, director general of the Protocol Department of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs; and Mr. Takashi Tajima, ambassador of Japan.
